      "review_summary": "The branch preserves valid JUnit summaries beside malformed reports, bounds auto-discovered report collection, adds opt-in fail-on-test-failures flag/config/env support, updates tests and docs, and edits CHANGELOG.md.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main source shows explicit JUnit parsing still fails fast on one malformed file and auto discovery still truncates candidate reports at 1 MiB before filtering, although I did not run an end-to-end lease during this read-only review.",
